WEBVTT

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:40.119
Your Highness, everything is arranged.

00:00:40.359 --> 00:00:41.359
On Wangyue Street,

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:42.920
the plan is in place.

00:00:45.560 --> 00:00:46.320
Tomorrow,

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:48.840
I will force Jiang Zhu to reveal herself.

00:00:49.439 --> 00:00:50.840
Once she is in danger,

00:00:51.479 --> 00:00:52.640
Imperial Uncle won't be able to resist.

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.119
He'll move to save her on instinct.

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.560
At that moment, the whole city

00:00:57.880 --> 00:01:00.039
will witness Prince Yan, Shen Miao,

00:01:00.200 --> 00:01:01.799
colluding with a Jade Waist Slave.

00:01:06.400 --> 00:01:07.599
You want to hurt Jiang Zhu,

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:10.200
and use her to deal with the prince?

00:01:18.000 --> 00:01:19.359
She was a Jade Waist Slave.

00:01:20.159 --> 00:01:21.640
That is exactly why she can be used.

00:01:22.239 --> 00:01:24.519
Could it be you invited Jiang Zhu to your birthday banquet?

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:27.319
to prove who she is?

00:01:27.640 --> 00:01:28.439
Yes.

00:01:29.480 --> 00:01:31.519
Now that you know her identity.

00:01:31.640 --> 00:01:33.359
then you should also see clearly

00:01:33.519 --> 00:01:35.040
what she means to Imperial Uncle.

00:01:37.640 --> 00:01:39.239
So you wanted me to be the Flower Goddess.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:42.159
just to make Jiang Zhu the Flower Attendant

00:01:42.319 --> 00:01:42.959
and set them up?

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:44.439
Yes. I set them up.

00:01:44.920 --> 00:01:47.239
It was Shen Miao who kept bullying me.

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:49.599
Between you

00:01:50.079 --> 00:01:51.079
Or the throne.

00:01:51.439 --> 00:01:52.439
which one matters more?

00:01:53.840 --> 00:01:55.920
I won't let him take either.

00:01:56.200 --> 00:01:57.359
And Crimson?

00:01:58.079 --> 00:01:59.599
She's been saving you ever since she appeared.

00:01:59.640 --> 00:02:00.879
I have never hurt you.

00:02:01.159 --> 00:02:02.200
You want revenge on Shen Miao,

00:02:02.239 --> 00:02:03.799
so you'll kill her too?

00:02:04.760 --> 00:02:06.680
Are you still the Shen Yuheng I know?

00:02:09.080 --> 00:02:11.479
Even if I really did know her when we were children.

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:14.280
But she is now a Jade Waist Slave.

00:02:15.360 --> 00:02:16.360
And I...

00:02:16.639 --> 00:02:18.319
am the Crown Prince of Great Yan.

00:02:19.280 --> 00:02:20.159
Kill her.

00:02:20.560 --> 00:02:21.479
Use her.

00:02:22.319 --> 00:02:23.560
What's wrong with that?

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:29.120
So the one before me

00:02:29.319 --> 00:02:30.439
is the Crown Prince,

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:32.360
Not Shen Yuheng.

00:02:33.159 --> 00:02:34.599
I spoke out of turn, Your Highness.

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:35.800
I overestimated myself.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:38.960
I mistook Your Highness for a confidant.

00:02:47.919 --> 00:02:48.439
Your legs...

00:02:48.479 --> 00:02:49.479
Why can Shen Miao

00:02:49.960 --> 00:02:51.639
hold a place in your heart,

00:02:52.599 --> 00:02:53.759
and Crimson too,

00:02:54.560 --> 00:02:55.479
but not me?

00:02:56.000 --> 00:02:57.439
I want to be accepted by you.

00:02:58.400 --> 00:02:59.400
In the end,

00:03:00.560 --> 00:03:02.800
I was only

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:04.280
a fabricated confidant.

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:15.960
What happened to Your Highness?

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:19.919
Get out.

00:03:26.520 --> 00:03:27.719
Before the Flower Festival,

00:03:28.719 --> 00:03:29.960
You are not allowed to go anywhere.

00:03:34.599 --> 00:03:35.439
From today on,

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:38.159
I will give you special training as the Flower Goddess.

00:03:39.639 --> 00:03:41.879
It's just archery, isn't it?

00:03:46.879 --> 00:03:47.879
It went off course again.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:48.879
If this goes on,

00:03:48.919 --> 00:03:50.080
how will I coordinate with Sister Zhaohua?

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:51.719
The flower ball will miss the mark,

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:53.680
and the blessing rite will fail.

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:57.879
At least it wasn't too far off.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:03:58.759
It doesn't matter.

00:03:58.960 --> 00:03:59.759
Let me teach you.

00:04:00.719 --> 00:04:01.680
Can you really teach me?

00:04:07.039 --> 00:04:07.759
Remember.

00:04:08.680 --> 00:04:09.919
As long as the bow is in your hand.

00:04:10.240 --> 00:04:11.639
Relax your body.

00:04:12.080 --> 00:04:13.439
Keep your emotions stable.

00:04:13.560 --> 00:04:14.120
Lock onto the target,

00:04:14.159 --> 00:04:15.039
Be firm.

00:04:24.319 --> 00:04:26.160
The Prince of Yan arrived.

00:04:31.639 --> 00:04:33.040
The Crown Prince has been in a wheelchair for years.

00:04:33.680 --> 00:04:35.560
Is his archery skill up to par?

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:49.399
The Crown Prince took this Flower Festival

00:04:49.759 --> 00:04:51.000
very seriously.

00:04:51.439 --> 00:04:52.879
A mere flower goddess.

00:04:53.319 --> 00:04:55.199
Does the Crown Prince really need to personally teach him?

00:04:55.399 --> 00:04:56.120
Better.

00:04:57.240 --> 00:04:58.639
Let me teach you first.

00:04:58.920 --> 00:05:00.120
As for Imperial Uncle,

00:05:00.879 --> 00:05:02.560
People who never set foot in the Bichen Palace.

00:05:02.920 --> 00:05:04.920
yet for a mere Flower Attendant

00:05:05.319 --> 00:05:06.639
you've already come twice.

00:05:07.519 --> 00:05:09.560
I really benefited from Jiang Zhu's influence.

00:05:21.279 --> 00:05:23.160
The Crown Prince sits here practicing archery each day.

00:05:23.279 --> 00:05:25.120
Then I should all the more hope you stand soon

00:05:25.160 --> 00:05:26.560
and face me directly.

00:05:27.079 --> 00:05:28.360
Don't let this arrow go astray

00:05:28.920 --> 00:05:29.920
and hurt someone.

00:05:33.519 --> 00:05:34.639
Imperial Uncle is overthinking it.

00:05:35.279 --> 00:05:36.199
Yuheng.

00:05:36.759 --> 00:05:38.959
Always going straight to the target.

00:05:42.199 --> 00:05:43.560
and never harm the innocent.

00:05:48.199 --> 00:05:50.160
Their uncle-nephew bond...

00:05:50.759 --> 00:05:53.079
I did not know it was this strained.

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:57.759
Where are you taking me?

00:06:00.639 --> 00:06:01.800
I have something to give you.

00:06:04.600 --> 00:06:06.319
You didn't steal something from the palace again, did you?

00:06:12.279 --> 00:06:13.040
This is a heart-protecting pill.

00:06:13.079 --> 00:06:14.360
The Flower Festival is near.

00:06:14.399 --> 00:06:15.560
What if I encounter danger?

00:06:15.639 --> 00:06:16.319
You take it.

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:18.319
It will suppress your instinct to rush out and save me.

00:06:21.120 --> 00:06:22.759
Are you asking me to just let you do whatever you want?

00:06:24.279 --> 00:06:25.560
Are you worried about me?

00:06:27.240 --> 00:06:28.480
I told you, you're just stubborn.

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:29.319
If it were before.

00:06:29.360 --> 00:06:30.839
You snatched it from me a long time ago.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:32.160
I have.

00:06:32.759 --> 00:06:33.759
This heart-protecting pill

00:06:33.800 --> 00:06:35.199
Each Jade Waist Slave has only one.

00:06:35.279 --> 00:06:36.160
Extremely precious.

00:06:36.319 --> 00:06:37.240
You should keep it safe.

00:06:37.439 --> 00:06:38.199
I'm leaving now.

00:06:39.319 --> 00:06:40.240
Where are you going again?

00:06:43.959 --> 00:06:44.800
Archery practice.

00:06:54.959 --> 00:06:56.800
You've worked hard these past few days.

00:06:57.360 --> 00:06:58.600
Today is a big day.

00:06:59.959 --> 00:07:01.560
I am truly grateful for your help.

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:02.519
He, Zhaohua...

00:07:13.480 --> 00:07:15.360
I agreed to be Flower Attendant

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:17.519
not for Sister Zhaohua,

00:07:17.920 --> 00:07:19.360
nor for you, Your Highness.

00:07:20.839 --> 00:07:23.240
I am doing this for the Little Auspicious Cloud from twelve years ago.

00:07:29.279 --> 00:07:30.600
According to the Imperial Uncle's temperament.

00:07:31.079 --> 00:07:32.639
He definitely tried to stop you from entering the palace.

00:07:35.879 --> 00:07:37.519
Why do you still believe me?

00:07:38.519 --> 00:07:40.240
Is it just because I saved you?

00:07:41.959 --> 00:07:42.759
No.

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:45.240
I trust you.

00:07:45.680 --> 00:07:48.120
Not just because of the Little Auspicious Cloud twelve years ago.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:50.680
but because of the man the Crown Prince became.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.519
From our first meeting after the reunion,

00:07:54.120 --> 00:07:55.920
He was risking his life to save people.

00:07:56.839 --> 00:07:59.279
A Crown Prince who cherishes common lives

00:07:59.480 --> 00:08:00.639
He can't be a bad person.

00:08:09.560 --> 00:08:11.040
This is what I believe.

00:08:21.480 --> 00:08:23.240
So beautiful!

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:28.439
So beautiful.

00:08:29.399 --> 00:08:30.680
The Flower Goddess is so beautiful this year!

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:32.600
Yes, like a celestial being.

00:08:33.399 --> 00:08:34.000
Yes.

00:08:42.279 --> 00:08:44.080
Nothing in this life comes easy for me.

00:08:44.919 --> 00:08:46.399
Yet this is all my own doing.

00:08:47.080 --> 00:08:48.559
He could have taken her home.

00:08:49.000 --> 00:08:50.519
But he insisted on keeping her by his side.

00:08:50.679 --> 00:08:51.360
Your Highness.

00:08:54.399 --> 00:08:55.039
Prince.

00:08:55.120 --> 00:08:56.960
Since you refuse the heart-protecting pill,

00:08:57.120 --> 00:08:58.159
Let's have some food first.

00:08:58.480 --> 00:08:59.639
Who said I was not eating?

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:02.480
You never intended to use this thing.

00:09:02.720 --> 00:09:03.879
what exactly worries you?

00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:05.159
I still have not found a good answer.

00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:07.399
for whatever may change tomorrow.

00:09:07.799 --> 00:09:08.440
This time,

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:09.600
the danger is not only from the palace.

00:09:09.679 --> 00:09:11.480
Getting someone out will not be simple.

00:09:13.240 --> 00:09:14.639
You watched me grow up.

00:09:15.159 --> 00:09:16.600
Nothing can be hidden from you.

00:09:18.039 --> 00:09:18.919
But.

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:21.440
I've practically watched Shen Yuheng grow up.

00:09:22.279 --> 00:09:23.159
Why.

00:09:24.679 --> 00:09:26.240
I understand him less and less.

00:09:28.399 --> 00:09:29.240
The prince ordered:

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:30.600
There will be crowds today.

00:09:30.720 --> 00:09:32.039
No mistakes.

00:09:32.720 --> 00:09:34.159
If you spot anyone suspicious,

00:09:34.360 --> 00:09:35.440
Inform me immediately.

00:09:35.919 --> 00:09:36.600
Yes.

00:09:42.320 --> 00:09:43.799
Before the start of the Flower Festival ceremony.

00:09:44.360 --> 00:09:45.919
Let Jiang Zhu drink this wine.

00:09:48.759 --> 00:09:49.519
Steward.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:51.000
Put the wine down.

00:09:52.559 --> 00:09:53.639
Send it out.

00:09:57.440 --> 00:09:58.879
Shijin, you go out first.

00:09:59.279 --> 00:10:00.559
I have something to say to the Crown Prince.

00:10:10.200 --> 00:10:11.000
Qin Zhaohua.

00:10:11.080 --> 00:10:11.960
Shen Yuheng.

00:10:16.679 --> 00:10:18.559
For a promise made in childhood,

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:21.919
Jiang Zhu risked her life to come find you.

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.600
She is the Jade Waist Slave.

00:10:25.720 --> 00:10:27.759
Jade Waist Slave slaughtered the army camp back then.

00:10:27.919 --> 00:10:28.799
yet neither of us saw her do it.

00:10:28.840 --> 00:10:30.639
I saw her do that with my own eyes.

00:10:31.960 --> 00:10:33.279
I only know Jiangzhu.

00:10:33.759 --> 00:10:35.720
All I know is that she has always been protecting us.

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.759
No matter what decision you ultimately make.

00:10:44.399 --> 00:10:46.600
I will do anything to protect her.

00:10:52.080 --> 00:10:53.039
And you...

00:10:55.919 --> 00:10:56.919
Yuheng Star.

00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:59.279
It is the brightest star in the Big Dipper.

00:11:01.240 --> 00:11:03.080
I remember Shen Yuheng, whom I fell in love with.

00:11:03.519 --> 00:11:05.320
He would risk his life to save a cat,

00:11:06.080 --> 00:11:07.559
and protect punished palace servants.

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:10.399
He once shone as brightly as the Yuheng Star.

00:11:10.960 --> 00:11:13.039
I can't let him be covered by dark clouds.

00:11:58.559 --> 00:11:59.799
Why have you not loosed the arrow?

00:12:00.639 --> 00:12:01.919
If the pom-pom lands directly...

00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:03.000
It's considered unlucky.

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:04.600
it means a grave omen for next year.

00:12:04.759 --> 00:12:06.960
Everyone, look at the face of the Flower Goddess!

00:12:09.960 --> 00:12:11.120
How is that possible?

00:12:15.879 --> 00:12:16.639
What happened?

00:12:16.759 --> 00:12:17.639
What is happening?

00:12:17.840 --> 00:12:19.080
Why aren't you shooting arrows yet?

00:12:19.639 --> 00:12:21.279
The flower ball is about to fall off.

00:12:21.679 --> 00:12:22.840
What should we do?

00:12:23.240 --> 00:12:24.480
This is bad!

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:34.519
Shoot, quickly!

00:12:34.799 --> 00:12:36.039
It's about to fall.

00:13:51.320 --> 00:13:52.279
Leave the rest to me.

00:13:52.440 --> 00:13:53.120
You should hurry up and leave.

00:13:55.840 --> 00:13:56.639
Take her away, now.

00:13:57.799 --> 00:13:58.360
Crimson.

00:13:58.480 --> 00:13:59.360
It's up to you now.

00:14:00.879 --> 00:14:01.559
Go.

00:14:01.559 --> 00:14:02.559
MkvDrama.Net